Package org.apache.pekko.dispatch

Interface UnboundedMessageQueueSemantics

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    UnboundedControlAwareMessageQueueSemantics, UnboundedDequeBasedMessageQueue, UnboundedDequeBasedMessageQueueSemantics, UnboundedQueueBasedMessageQueue
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NodeMessageQueue, UnboundedControlAwareMailbox.MessageQueue, UnboundedDequeBasedMailbox.MessageQueue, UnboundedMailbox.MessageQueue, UnboundedPriorityMailbox.MessageQueue, UnboundedStablePriorityMailbox.MessageQueue
    public interface UnboundedMessageQueueSemantics
    UnboundedMessageQueueSemantics adds unbounded semantics to a QueueBasedMessageQueue, i.e. a non-blocking enqueue and dequeue.
